  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, mix together semolina flour, water, and yogurt to form a smooth batter.",
    "Let the batter ferment for 24 hours in a warm place.",
    "Heat ghee in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and coriander seeds and let them sizzle for 1 minute.",
    "Add turmeric and salt and stir well.",
    "Add the fermented batter to the pan and stir constantly.",
